{{Nihongo|'''''Live'''''|ライヴ}} is a 2014 Japanese [[horror film|horror]] [[mystery film|mystery]] [[suspense film|suspense]] film directed by [[Noboru Iguchi]] and starring [[Yuki Yamada]] which was released on 10 May, 2014.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://twitchfilm.com/2014/04/race-from-death-with-full-trailer-for-iguchis-live.html|title= Race From Death With Full Trailer For Iguchi's LIVE|author= Todd Brown|date= 14 April 2014|accessdate= 3 May 2014|work= [[Twitch Film]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.allcinema.net/prog/show_c.php?num_c=348416|script-title=ja:ライヴ (2014)|accessdate= 3 May 2014|work= allcinema.net|publisher= Stingray|language= Japanese}}</ref>

